.description
Can read an RDB and save it to a file, as for backup purpose,
and write it back later on the hard disk. Gives also the
state of the reselection flag and all rdb_Flags.
New FORCE switch. 
Bug under --2.x--, unable to write back an RDB, fixed, oops!
